  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Nominated for multiple VR Game of the Year awards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Floor Plan 2</strong> is a comedy adventure inspired by escape rooms, packed with more puzzles than you can fit in an elevator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your first day of work, the boss sends you to find a lost treasure that will turn the company's fortunes around. And good news: it's somewhere in the building! Just use the elevator down the hall. By the way, each floor is a gateway to another world, nobody speaks your language, and time and space are fluid. Good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/6495e502a36961916df15367da81938e.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/6495e502a36961916df15367da81938e.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/6495e502a36961916df15367da81938e.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HILARIOUS, MIND-BENDING PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your elevator to explore a series of interconnected escape rooms. Step out onto each floor, meet bizarre characters, and unravel their secrets. Revisit completed floors to find new, remixed challenges waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/1bcbe295d4c19f3b940393e6ee58bb96.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/1bcbe295d4c19f3b940393e6ee58bb96.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/1bcbe295d4c19f3b940393e6ee58bb96.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HAND PRESENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Red Harrys, lost critters hidden throughout the building, to earn hand presents and transform your hands in all sorts of unexpected ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/711012364456f4309d55ad90e5d44502.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/711012364456f4309d55ad90e5d44502.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/711012364456f4309d55ad90e5d44502.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >6+ HOURS OF HANDCRAFTED GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Filled with critically-acclaimed puzzles and memorable \"aha!\" moments that respect your time and intelligence. Now includes the Backside Story expansion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/5d9b3b68ca02e656af0d88a5a81ae300.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/5d9b3b68ca02e656af0d88a5a81ae300.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/5d9b3b68ca02e656af0d88a5a81ae300.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHARMING-AS-HECK WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built for VR, comfortable for everyone, and developed with love by the small but mighty Turbo Button team.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Nominated for multiple VR Game of the Year awards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Floor Plan 2</strong> is a comedy adventure inspired by escape rooms, packed with more puzzles than you can fit in an elevator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your first day of work, the boss sends you to find a lost treasure that will turn the company's fortunes around. And good news: it's somewhere in the building! Just use the elevator down the hall. By the way, each floor is a gateway to another world, nobody speaks your language, and time and space are fluid. Good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/6495e502a36961916df15367da81938e.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/6495e502a36961916df15367da81938e.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/6495e502a36961916df15367da81938e.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HILARIOUS, MIND-BENDING PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your elevator to explore a series of interconnected escape rooms. Step out onto each floor, meet bizarre characters, and unravel their secrets. Revisit completed floors to find new, remixed challenges waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/1bcbe295d4c19f3b940393e6ee58bb96.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/1bcbe295d4c19f3b940393e6ee58bb96.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/1bcbe295d4c19f3b940393e6ee58bb96.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HAND PRESENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Red Harrys, lost critters hidden throughout the building, to earn hand presents and transform your hands in all sorts of unexpected ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/711012364456f4309d55ad90e5d44502.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/711012364456f4309d55ad90e5d44502.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/711012364456f4309d55ad90e5d44502.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >6+ HOURS OF HANDCRAFTED GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Filled with critically-acclaimed puzzles and memorable \"aha!\" moments that respect your time and intelligence. Now includes the Backside Story expansion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/5d9b3b68ca02e656af0d88a5a81ae300.poster.avif?t=1757354275\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/5d9b3b68ca02e656af0d88a5a81ae300.webm?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534850/extras/5d9b3b68ca02e656af0d88a5a81ae300.mp4?t=1757354275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHARMING-AS-HECK WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built for VR, comfortable for everyone, and developed with love by the small but mighty Turbo Button team.</p>",
